    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/c1d67263f324642c068e3b2d69d2ae2a.poster.avif?t=1646423701\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/c1d67263f324642c068e3b2d69d2ae2a.webm?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/c1d67263f324642c068e3b2d69d2ae2a.mp4?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《布莱尔女巫——虚拟现实版》（Blair Witch: VR Edition）是一款由情节推动的心理恐怖游戏，灵感源自恐怖大片《布莱尔女巫》。你将扮演背负心灵创伤的前任警官埃利斯，在美国马里兰州柏莱克镇的布莱克山森林参与搜寻一名失踪的男孩。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/81718f52f1dfda10e5c32410d75d1f20.poster.avif?t=1646423701\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/81718f52f1dfda10e5c32410d75d1f20.webm?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/81718f52f1dfda10e5c32410d75d1f20.mp4?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>看似普通的调查转瞬间成了一场梦魇，迫使你去面对布莱尔女巫与内心深处的恐惧。不过你并不是独自一人，值得信赖的警犬搭档“子弹”会伴你左右，在凶险恐怖的丛林中成为你的耳目。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/83f0298a9b5587836002a94f7e2a257b.poster.avif?t=1646423701\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/83f0298a9b5587836002a94f7e2a257b.webm?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/83f0298a9b5587836002a94f7e2a257b.mp4?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>游戏专为VR版重新打造，将通过虚拟现实带给玩家独特的沉浸式恐怖体验。游戏环境针对互动性重新设计，与子弹互动时新增了手势指令、逼真的抚摸等操作方式。你还会遭遇更多敌人，在布莱克山森林体验到前所未有的恐怖气氛。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/33fc9207b1d667b48f48db70614ac4a9.poster.avif?t=1646423701\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/33fc9207b1d667b48f48db70614ac4a9.webm?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/33fc9207b1d667b48f48db70614ac4a9.mp4?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>这片受到诅咒的丛林将会唤醒你内心最深层的恐惧。",
